{"tid":1020923,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曝祖記欲2億歐砸埃及王牌巨星 獲C.朗拿度支持","createTime":"2019-02-14T02:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T18:41:39.000Z","uid":147522,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec735e4fa4d5907dacba414cbd669afc8b50543","tid":1020923,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T02:18:14.000Z","msg":"　　繼正式宣佈簽下阿仙奴中場大將藍斯後，祖記又將視線轉向了另一名英超巨星，利物浦前鋒沙拿。<br />\n<br />\n　　據阿拉伯天空體育消息，祖記準備花2億歐元簽下沙拿。報導中稱，這一決定也獲得了祖記頭號球星C.朗拿度的支持，葡萄牙人已經為球會高層「開綠燈」。如果祖記真的以2億歐元的價格引進沙拿，那麼埃及人在球壇轉會費排行榜上將僅次於尼馬，成為歷史第二高。<br />\n<br />\n　　不過在祖記為簽下沙拿所開出的條件上，意大利《拖連奴體育報》則給出了不同的說法，他們表示祖記準備用戴巴拿+5000萬歐元換取沙拿。"},{"pid":"05fd42437eb8fbf2c59c6ab64a5cc5f56711be1c","tid":1020923,"uid":36372,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T02:19:39.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙人已經為球會高層「開綠燈」 啱啱黎就處理埋轉會"},{"pid":"50fa5f90f5b7c0199a09804144cfb256b661e72d","tid":1020923,"uid":68,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T02:26:39.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"46f6d089c8f90ddf6f4fcc3399d66d370c7490f1","tid":1020923,"uid":230544,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T02:27:33.000Z","msg":"利下季又可以有盈利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2a9afafba65578245d3e944ecd12f535dff2e9","tid":1020923,"uid":72647,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"on9 先換走戴巴拿"},{"pid":"54b4b76bfdf791a85578754abf035fd56a524d86","tid":1020923,"uid":151324,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"